trans-unit.source: This method does not validate or modify the specified `printTicket` for a particular <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden ikke validere eller endre den angitte `printTicket` for en bestemt <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>

trans-unit.source: If necessary, use the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A> method to create a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> that is specific to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> and is valid for a specified printer.
trans-unit.target: Bruk eventuelt den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>metode for å opprette en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>som er spesifikk for de <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>og er gyldig for en angitt skriver.</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.MergeAndValidatePrintTicket%2A>
